Biljana McKinley (CRD# 4796237) is an Investment Advisor Representative working at Evermay Wealth Management, LLC in Arlington, VA and has over 13 years of experience in the finance industry.As a wealth advisor, Biljana serves many of Evermay’s high net worth clients. Prior to Evermay, Biljana served as an assistant vice president and wealth advisor at United Bank for more than six years. She holds a B.A. in Business Administration magna cum laude from Texas Lutheran University, graduating in 2003, and earned her Certified Financial Planner (CFP) designation from Georgetown University in 2008. Biljana holds a Virginia life and annuity insurance license and is also a chapter member of the Women Presidents’ Organization. She resides in Vienna, Virginia with her husband and two daughters.





